<br>
5 clerics, 25 meeles<br>
<br>
spawn general<br>
<br>
pull general single<br>
<br>
hit autoattack <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br>
