Depending on your level, you may need more or less.  He procs a 500 dd spell and is nasty.  You will need to get him to spread out his damage enough so that the clerics have time to heal everyone.  This is a point where AE heals shine, but only if a few people manage to draw attention in the group.  NO ONE wants too much attention, so everyone should taunt so he keeps switching targets.<br>
<br>
DO NOT let him ping pong, if he gets up on a wall he is gonna take your guys out one at a time, and the more he moves the less people can hit him.<br>
