<br>
Once we regrouped, things went much smoother the second time around.  We made sure the main tank had plenty of aggro (kinda funny to watch a swarm of melee classes foaming at the mouth, wanting to jump in the battle, and being told to wait <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )  After that, everyone jumped in and spanked the General down with very little trouble. <p>-----------------------------------------------<BR>
